Advantages and Disadvantages
Agile Advantages- Rapid delivery- High adaptability- Strong collaboration- Early issue detection- High customer satisfaction
Agile Disadvantages- Less predictability- Requires skilled teams- Minimal documentation
Waterfall Advantages- Clear structure- Easy management- Detailed documentation- Predictable schedules
Waterfall Disadvantages- Inflexible- Late error detection- Limited feedback- Poor fit for changing requirements
Conclusion
